data.description: Welcome to Hickory Pointe!  This beautiful ranch style home will leave you in awe.  The well manicured lawn produces amazing curb appeal.  The front of the house is covered with stack stone accents.  The open concept floor plan features soaring ceilings, split bedrooms, beautiful architecture, private owners suite with/oversized bedroom, double sinks, built in shelves, and soaking tub.  The gallery style kitchen features a breakfast bar.  This home features a 2 car garage. The backyard offers a spacious patio and a workshop which could also be used as a playhouse. There are some areas of the home that could use some touch up painting. Bring your buyers! Show and Sell!!
